episodes.title: Eckankar: The Midwestern Cult You’ve Never Heard Of
episodes.description:
Eckankar looks like a harmless meditation practice, but there’s a deeper story behind it. This video uncovers the origins of the movement and the cult claims surrounding it.


View the unedited interview with David C. Lane: https://youtu.be/AfpS9x1trBA?si=6I68C4AZx5lBQVE7
